name: High-fidelity Prototyping with weave.ly
description:
Your design, with real data, running on real devices, validated by real users.

------------------------------------------------------------

This file helps you get started with the weave.ly plugin. More concretely it contains:


  • A set of getting started tutorials to get you familiar with the plugin and its functionality
  • A design kit with pre-built components which you can use to rapidly build functional high-fidelity prototypes


------------------------------------------------------------

If you're stuck, have any questions or general remarks feel free to reach out via info@weave.ly
